<figureCitation box="[921,977,809,832]" captionStart="FIGURES 5–8" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1927,1952]" captionTargetBox="[151,1429,196,1890]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[151,1436,196,1890]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 5–8. Heads and pronota of Peripus Chatzimanolis &amp; Hightower. 5. Peripus brunkei Chatzimanolis &amp; Hightower. 6. Peripus didontus Chatzimanolis &amp; Hightower. 7. Peripus madrededios Chatzimanolis &amp; Hightower. 8. Peripus monodontus Chatzimanolis &amp; Hightower. Not to scale." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3354780/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="383">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
)......................... 
